TEXT.S: = Paran = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Jnaysyang ka alang paran. 686 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,940 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 30% niqan 590 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 70% niqan 1,350 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq17%, Tayal10%, Bunun2%, Paiwan1%.
